description:
Not many doctrines have tormented Christians more than the doctrine of Hell. Just the idea of hell can send shivers down ones spine. But what is hell? Is it to be separated from God? Is it eternal punishment and conscious torment, or is it a time when one simply ceases to exist? What about the love of God, where does that come into it? You can find the answers to all of these questions and much more in the next presentation, The Desolation. Watch it now @ awr.org/bible.
